{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":581,"text":"I'm a man who's trying to live from his heart,"},{"time":4289,"text":"and so just before I get going,"},{"time":7354,"text":"I wanted to tell you as a South African"},{"time":9925,"text":"that one of the men who has inspired me most"},{"time":12909,"text":"passed away a few hours ago."},{"time":15975,"text":"Nelson Mandela has come to the end"},{"time":18665,"text":"of his long walk to freedom."},{"time":21345,"text":"And so this talk is going to be for him."}]},{"cues":[{"time":28544,"text":"I grew up in wonder."},{"time":31354,"text":"I grew up amongst those animals."},{"time":35469,"text":"I grew up in the wild eastern part of South Africa"},{"time":39860,"text":"at a place called Londolozi Game Reserve."},{"time":42758,"text":"It's a place where my family has been"},{"time":45530,"text":"in the safari business for four generations."},{"time":49725,"text":"Now for as long as I can remember,"},{"time":51962,"text":"my job has been to take people out into nature,"},{"time":56699,"text":"and so I think it's a lovely twist of fate today"},{"time":59610,"text":"to have the opportunity"},{"time":61430,"text":"to bring some of my experiences out in nature"},{"time":64311,"text":"in to this gathering."},{"time":66451,"text":"Africa is a place"},{"time":68330,"text":"where people still sit under starlit skies"},{"time":71714,"text":"and around campfires and tell stories,"},{"time":75124,"text":"and so what I have to share with you today"},{"time":77815,"text":"is the simple medicine of a few campfire stories,"},{"time":82234,"text":"stories about heroes of heart."},{"time":85372,"text":"Now my stories are not the stories"},{"time":87492,"text":"that you'll hear on the news,"},{"time":89190,"text":"and while it's true that Africa is a harsh place,"},{"time":92163,"text":"I also know it to be a place"},{"time":94100,"text":"where people, animals and ecosystems"},{"time":98366,"text":"teach us about a more interconnected world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":102753,"text":"When I was nine years old,"},{"time":104731,"text":"President Mandela came to stay with my family."},{"time":107965,"text":"He had just been released from\nhis 27 years of incarceration,"},{"time":111389,"text":"and was in a period of readjustment"},{"time":114016,"text":"to his sudden global icon status."},{"time":116675,"text":"Members of the African National Congress"},{"time":119175,"text":"thought that in the bush"},{"time":121166,"text":"he would have time to rest and recuperate"},{"time":123400,"text":"away from the public eye,"},{"time":125161,"text":"and it's true that lions tend to be"},{"time":128540,"text":"a very good deterrent to press and paparazzi."},{"time":132771,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":134900,"text":"But it was a defining time for me as a young boy."},{"time":137446,"text":"I would take him breakfast in bed,"},{"time":139507,"text":"and then, in an old track suit and slippers,"},{"time":141875,"text":"he would go for a walk around the garden."},{"time":144480,"text":"At night, I would sit with my family"},{"time":146158,"text":"around the snowy, bunny-eared TV,"},{"time":148659,"text":"and watch images of that same"},{"time":151077,"text":"quiet man from the garden"},{"time":153011,"text":"surrounded by hundreds and thousands of people"},{"time":156061,"text":"as scenes from his release were broadcast nightly."},{"time":159320,"text":"He was bringing peace"},{"time":161272,"text":"to a divided and violent South Africa,"},{"time":164154,"text":"one man with an unbelievable sense of his humanity."},{"time":169383,"text":"Mandela said often that the gift of prison"},{"time":172147,"text":"was the ability to go within and to think,"},{"time":175107,"text":"to create in himself"},{"time":176836,"text":"the things he most wanted for South Africa:"},{"time":179715,"text":"peace, reconciliation, harmony."},{"time":183060,"text":"Through this act of immense open-heartedness,"},{"time":185915,"text":"he was to become the embodiment"},{"time":188147,"text":"of what in South Africa we call \"ubuntu.\""},{"time":191686,"text":"Ubuntu: I am because of you."},{"time":194535,"text":"Or, people are not people"},{"time":197198,"text":"without other people."},{"time":199923,"text":"It's not a new idea or value"},{"time":201769,"text":"but it's one that I certainly think at these times"},{"time":203624,"text":"is worth building on."},{"time":205373,"text":"In fact, it is said that in the\ncollective consciousness of Africa,"},{"time":208537,"text":"we get to experience the deepest parts"},{"time":210576,"text":"of our own humanity"},{"time":211881,"text":"through our interactions with others."},{"time":214665,"text":"Ubuntu is at play right now."},{"time":216777,"text":"You are holding a space for me"},{"time":218777,"text":"to express the deepest truth of who I am."},{"time":222169,"text":"Without you, I'm just a guy talking to an empty room,"},{"time":224429,"text":"and I spent a lot of time last week doing that,"},{"time":227507,"text":"and it's not the same as this."},{"time":230830,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":233256,"text":"If Mandela was the national\nand international embodiment,"},{"time":236704,"text":"then the man who taught me the most"},{"time":238298,"text":"about this value personally was this man,"},{"time":240901,"text":"Solly Mhlongo."},{"time":242259,"text":"Solly was born under a tree"},{"time":244067,"text":"60 kilometers from where I grew up in Mozambique."},{"time":246853,"text":"He would never have a lot of money,"},{"time":248353,"text":"but he was to be"},{"time":249775,"text":"one of the richest men I would ever meet."},{"time":252404,"text":"Solly grew up tending to his father's cattle."},{"time":255123,"text":"Now, I can tell you, I don't know what it is\nabout people who grow up looking after cattle,"},{"time":259305,"text":"but it makes for Ã¼ber-resourcefulness."},{"time":262327,"text":"The first job that he ever got in the safari business"},{"time":264801,"text":"was fixing the safari trucks."},{"time":267017,"text":"Where he had learned to do that out in the bush"},{"time":269671,"text":"I have no idea, but he could do it."},{"time":271800,"text":"He then moved across into what we called"},{"time":273727,"text":"the habitat team."},{"time":275114,"text":"These were the people on the reserve"},{"time":277000,"text":"who were responsible for its well-being."},{"time":279357,"text":"He fixed roads, he mended wetlands,"},{"time":281641,"text":"he did some anti-poaching."},{"time":283459,"text":"And then one day we were out together,"},{"time":285585,"text":"and he came across the tracks of where\na female leopard had walked."},{"time":289116,"text":"And it was an old track,"},{"time":290890,"text":"but for fun he turned and he began to follow it,"},{"time":293331,"text":"and I tell you, I could tell by the speed"},{"time":294906,"text":"at which he moved on those pad marks"},{"time":296603,"text":"that this man was a Ph.D.-level tracker."},{"time":300577,"text":"If you drove past Solly"},{"time":302351,"text":"somewhere out on the reserve,"},{"time":304029,"text":"you look up in your rearview mirror,"},{"time":305678,"text":"you'd see he'd stopped the car"},{"time":307523,"text":"20, 50 meters down the road"},{"time":309569,"text":"just in case you need help with something."},{"time":312582,"text":"The only accusation I ever heard leveled at him"},{"time":315335,"text":"was when one of our clients said,"},{"time":316730,"text":"\"Solly, you are pathologically helpful.\""},{"time":319947,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":322394,"text":"When I started professionally guiding people"},{"time":325285,"text":"out into this environment,"},{"time":326942,"text":"Solly was my tracker."},{"time":328502,"text":"We worked together as a team."},{"time":330321,"text":"And the first guests we ever got"},{"time":332347,"text":"were a philanthropy group from your East Coast,"},{"time":335194,"text":"and they said to Solly, on the side, they said,"},{"time":337548,"text":"\"Before we even go out to see lions and leopards,"},{"time":340189,"text":"we want to see where you live.\""},{"time":342251,"text":"So we took them up to his house,"},{"time":343716,"text":"and this visit of the philanthropist to his house"},{"time":346588,"text":"coincided with a time when Solly's wife,"},{"time":349269,"text":"who was learning English,"},{"time":350869,"text":"was going through a phase\nwhere she would open the door"},{"time":353053,"text":"by saying, \"Hello, I love you."},{"time":355717,"text":"Welcome, I love you.\" (Laughter)"},{"time":357932,"text":"And there was something so beautifully African"},{"time":360481,"text":"about it to me, this small house"},{"time":362326,"text":"with a huge heart in it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":364911,"text":"Now on the day that Solly saved my life,"},{"time":371486,"text":"he was already my hero."},{"time":373497,"text":"It was a hot day,"},{"time":375078,"text":"and we found ourselves down by the river."},{"time":377052,"text":"Because of the heat, I took my shoes off,"},{"time":379888,"text":"and I rolled up my pants,"},{"time":381591,"text":"and I walked into the water."},{"time":383832,"text":"Solly remained on the bank."},{"time":385394,"text":"The water was clear running over sand,"},{"time":388417,"text":"and we turned and we began\nto make our way upstream."},{"time":391731,"text":"And a few meters ahead of us,"},{"time":393551,"text":"there was a place where a tree\nhad fallen out of the bank,"},{"time":396536,"text":"and its branches were touching the water,"},{"time":399307,"text":"and it was shadowy."},{"time":400904,"text":"And if had been a horror movie,"},{"time":403362,"text":"people in the audience would have started saying,"},{"time":405598,"text":"\"Don't go in there. Don't go in there.\" (Laughter)"},{"time":409051,"text":"And of course, the crocodile was in the shadows."},{"time":412808,"text":"Now the first thing that you notice\nwhen a crocodile hits you"},{"time":414923,"text":"is the ferocity of the bite."},{"time":416523,"text":"Wham! It hits me by my right leg."},{"time":418496,"text":"It pulls me. It turns. I throw my hand up.\nI'm able to grab a branch."},{"time":422399,"text":"It's shaking me violently."},{"time":424137,"text":"It's a very strange sensation"},{"time":425851,"text":"having another creature try and eat you,"},{"time":427797,"text":"and there are few things that\npromote vegetarianism like that."},{"time":431248,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":432843,"text":"Solly on the bank sees that I'm in trouble."},{"time":435128,"text":"He turns. He begins to make his way to me."},{"time":437175,"text":"The croc again continues to shake me."},{"time":439126,"text":"It goes to bite me a second time."},{"time":441043,"text":"I notice a slick of blood in the water around me"},{"time":443232,"text":"that gets washed downstream."},{"time":444836,"text":"As it bites the second time, I kick."},{"time":447009,"text":"My foot goes down its throat. It spits me out."},{"time":449742,"text":"I pull myself up into the branches,"},{"time":451873,"text":"and as I come out of the water,\nI look over my shoulder."},{"time":455356,"text":"My leg from the knee down"},{"time":457276,"text":"is mangled beyond description."},{"time":459204,"text":"The bone is cracked."},{"time":460599,"text":"The meat is torn up."},{"time":462429,"text":"I make an instant decision that\nI'll never look at that again."},{"time":467029,"text":"As I come out of the water,"},{"time":469413,"text":"Solly arrives at a deep section,"},{"time":472030,"text":"a channel between us."},{"time":473655,"text":"He knows, he sees the state of my leg,"},{"time":475793,"text":"he knows that between him and I"},{"time":477639,"text":"there is a crocodile,"},{"time":478851,"text":"and I can tell you this man doesn't\nslow down for one second."},{"time":481343,"text":"He comes straight into the channel."},{"time":483149,"text":"He wades in to above his waist."},{"time":485084,"text":"He gets to me. He grabs me."},{"time":486547,"text":"I'm still in a vulnerable position."},{"time":488219,"text":"He picks me and puts me on his shoulder."},{"time":489944,"text":"This is the other thing about Solly,\nhe's freakishly strong."},{"time":492363,"text":"He turns. He walks me up the bank."},{"time":494826,"text":"He lays me down. He pulls his shirt off."},{"time":496880,"text":"He wraps it around my leg,"},{"time":498664,"text":"picks me up a second time,"},{"time":499955,"text":"walks me to a vehicle,"},{"time":501861,"text":"and he's able to get me to medical attention."},{"time":505285,"text":"And I survive."}]},{"cues":[{"time":508508,"text":"Now â (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":512769,"text":"Now I don't know how many people you know"},{"time":515479,"text":"that go into a deep channel of water"},{"time":517695,"text":"that they know has a crocodile in it"},{"time":519955,"text":"to come and help you,"},{"time":521298,"text":"but for Solly, it was as natural as breathing."},{"time":524742,"text":"And he is one amazing example"},{"time":527198,"text":"of what I have experienced all over Africa."},{"time":530643,"text":"In a more collective society,"},{"time":532774,"text":"we realize from the inside"},{"time":535622,"text":"that our own well-being is deeply tied"},{"time":538755,"text":"to the well-being of others."},{"time":541993,"text":"Danger is shared. Pain is shared."},{"time":545262,"text":"Joy is shared. Achievement is shared."},{"time":548187,"text":"Houses are shared. Food is shared."},{"time":552717,"text":"Ubuntu asks us to open our hearts"},{"time":555913,"text":"and to share,"},{"time":557327,"text":"and what Solly taught me that day"},{"time":559279,"text":"is the essence of this value,"},{"time":561282,"text":"his animated, empathetic action"},{"time":564040,"text":"in every moment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":566085,"text":"Now although the root word is about people,"},{"time":569592,"text":"I thought that maybe ubuntu was only about people."},{"time":572966,"text":"And then I met this young lady."},{"time":576240,"text":"Her name was Elvis."},{"time":577934,"text":"In fact, Solly gave her the name Elvis"},{"time":579705,"text":"because he said she walked like she was doing"},{"time":582562,"text":"the Elvis the pelvis dance."},{"time":585227,"text":"She was born with very badly\ndeformed back legs and pelvis."},{"time":589593,"text":"She arrived at our reserve from a reserve"},{"time":591857,"text":"east of us on her migratory route."},{"time":593913,"text":"When I first saw her,"},{"time":595692,"text":"I thought she would be dead in a matter of days."},{"time":598160,"text":"And yet, for the next five years"},{"time":601088,"text":"she returned in the winter months."},{"time":603618,"text":"And we would be so excited to be out in the bush"},{"time":605995,"text":"and to come across this unusual track."},{"time":608391,"text":"It looked like an inverted bracket,"},{"time":609886,"text":"and we would drop whatever\nwe were doing and we would follow,"},{"time":612335,"text":"and then we would come around the corner,"},{"time":614006,"text":"and there she would be with her herd."},{"time":616092,"text":"And that outpouring of emotion"},{"time":618987,"text":"from people on our safari trucks"},{"time":620701,"text":"as they saw her, it was this sense of kinship."},{"time":623943,"text":"And it reminded me"},{"time":625428,"text":"that even people who grow up in cities"},{"time":627359,"text":"feel a natural connection"},{"time":630944,"text":"with the natural world and with animals."},{"time":633215,"text":"And yet still I remained amazed\nthat she was surviving."},{"time":636799,"text":"And then one day we came across\nthem at this small water hole."},{"time":639760,"text":"It was sort of a hollow in the ground."},{"time":641612,"text":"And I watched as the matriarch drank,"},{"time":644066,"text":"and then she turned in that \nbeautiful slow motion of elephants,"},{"time":647341,"text":"looks like the arm in motion,"},{"time":649110,"text":"and she began to make her way up the steep bank."},{"time":652116,"text":"The rest of the herd turned and began to follow."},{"time":656760,"text":"And I watched young Elvis"},{"time":658544,"text":"begin to psych herself up for the hill."},{"time":661900,"text":"She got visibly -- ears came forward,"},{"time":665255,"text":"she had a full go of it and halfway up,"},{"time":667404,"text":"her legs gave way, and she fell backwards."},{"time":669681,"text":"She attempted it a second time,"},{"time":671500,"text":"and again, halfway up, she fell backwards."},{"time":674675,"text":"And on the third attempt,"},{"time":676532,"text":"an amazing thing happened."},{"time":678989,"text":"Halfway up the bank,"},{"time":680726,"text":"a young teenage elephant came in behind her,"},{"time":683799,"text":"and he propped his trunk underneath her,"},{"time":686002,"text":"and he began to shovel her up the bank."},{"time":689339,"text":"And it occurred to me"},{"time":690727,"text":"that the rest of the herd"},{"time":692283,"text":"was in fact looking after this young elephant."},{"time":694958,"text":"The next day I watched again"},{"time":697482,"text":"as the matriarch broke a branch"},{"time":699652,"text":"and she would put it in her mouth,"},{"time":701493,"text":"and then she would break a second one"},{"time":703450,"text":"and drop it on the ground."},{"time":706157,"text":"And a consensus developed between all of us"},{"time":708529,"text":"who were guiding people in that area"},{"time":710378,"text":"that that herd was in fact moving slower"},{"time":713527,"text":"to accommodate that elephant."}]},{"cues":[{"time":717583,"text":"What Elvis and the herd taught me"},{"time":719674,"text":"caused me to expand my definition of ubuntu,"},{"time":722998,"text":"and I believe that in the cathedral of the wild,"},{"time":725614,"text":"we get to see the most beautiful parts of ourselves"},{"time":727825,"text":"reflected back at us."},{"time":729582,"text":"And it is not only through other people"},{"time":733222,"text":"that we get to experience our humanity"},{"time":736142,"text":"but through all the creatures that live on this planet."},{"time":740068,"text":"If Africa has a gift to share,"},{"time":742882,"text":"it's a gift of a more collective society."},{"time":746709,"text":"And while it's true that ubuntu is an African idea,"},{"time":750957,"text":"what I see is the essence of that value"},{"time":755368,"text":"being invented here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":757730,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":759845,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":784082,"text":"Pat Mitchell: So Boyd,"},{"time":785879,"text":"we know that you knew President Mandela"},{"time":790920,"text":"from early childhood"},{"time":792897,"text":"and that you heard the news as we all did today,"},{"time":795796,"text":"and deeply distraught"},{"time":798236,"text":"and know the tragic loss that it is to the world."},{"time":802667,"text":"But I just wondered if you wanted"},{"time":804749,"text":"to share any additional thoughts,"},{"time":806655,"text":"because we know that you heard that news"},{"time":808729,"text":"just before coming in to do this session."}]},{"cues":[{"time":812109,"text":"Boyd Varty: Well thanks, Pat."},{"time":813805,"text":"I'm so happy because it was time for him to pass on."},{"time":816988,"text":"He was suffering."},{"time":818759,"text":"And so of course there's the mixed emotions."},{"time":821157,"text":"But I just think of so many occurrences"},{"time":823141,"text":"like the time he went on the Oprah show"},{"time":825548,"text":"and asked her what the show would be about."},{"time":828404,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":829882,"text":"And she was like, \"Well, it'll be about you.\""},{"time":833180,"text":"I mean, that's just incredible humility."},{"time":835928,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":839591,"text":"He was the father of our nation"},{"time":842753,"text":"and we've got a road to walk in South Africa."},{"time":849201,"text":"And everything, they used to call it Madiba magic."},{"time":852611,"text":"You know, he used to go to\na rugby match and we would win."},{"time":855394,"text":"Anywhere he went, things went well."},{"time":858855,"text":"But I think that magic will be with us,"},{"time":861236,"text":"and the important thing is that we carry"},{"time":864797,"text":"what he stood for."},{"time":866322,"text":"And so that's what I'm going to try and do,"},{"time":869809,"text":"and that's what people all over \nSouth Africa are trying to do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":872701,"text":"PM: And that's what you've done today.\nBV: Oh, thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":874927,"text":"PM: Thank you.\nBV: Thank you. Thanks very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":878066,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}